{"tid":260680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果干地一直拎聯賽冠軍但係一隻盃都落唔到袋 可以教到幾多年?","createTime":"2017-05-27T19:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T03:15:56.000Z","uid":44748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d37b9f8ac83947ccca77eebd09761af48773a5f","tid":260680,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:41:36.000Z","msg":"大家都知道干地拎聯賽冠軍有一手 但係逢盃賽 歐聯都係唔識打 如果佢可以一直拎聯賽冠軍 但係所有獎盃都嬴唔到冠軍 而且歐聯賽事就好快輸 例如分組 16強已經88 咁樣既話如果干地係沒心走既情況下 佢會教多幾多年就會比人炒?<br />\n<br />\n大定不妨討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n我覺得5年啦 話哂聯賽冠軍有一定重要性"},{"pid":"bae9ba9addbf62ba0d53cf4c371405d6349d816b","tid":260680,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:43:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"745fb8aa6b88272ec7087ddc62b110ba344a54e7","tid":260680,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"以干地呢個勝利11人戰術，出年雙線作戰聯賽都難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e9327054f938ffd88629861572dd39d54d99e7","tid":260680,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以干地呢個勝利11人戰術，出年雙線作戰聯賽都難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好有呢個假設先 我想問既係班主會幾時先頂唔順一個淨係會拎到聯賽冠軍既教練?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57da4786bf543c407fc0977e1fa9956324a39ad5","tid":260680,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"448b18c93ba6ded1b35f6c2bb252cf3c5626603e","tid":260680,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以干地呢個勝利11人戰術，出年雙線作戰聯賽都難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好有呢個假設先 我想問既係班主會幾時先頂唔順一個淨係會拎到聯賽冠軍既教練?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote